    - Understand the relationship between quantum computing and classical cryptography.
    - Recall the relationship between AES 256 security level and RSA modulus size
    - Analyze the role of public key cryptography in key exchange phases
    - Apply knowledge of algorithms to determine the most efficient method for bulk
